jerklib.parsers

Class DefaultInternalEventParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • jerklib.parsers.DefaultInternalEventParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InternalEventParser

    public class DefaultInternalEventParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements InternalEventParser
    This is the default impl of InternalEventParser. This class is used to turn raw irc text into IRCEvents. You can change the parsing of data and the creation of events by adding/removing CommandParsers.
    Author:
    mohadib
